COMMANDS
------------
'r' Resource
lists resources contained in Stockpile

------------
's' Settlers
lists living settlers in Settlement

's X' displays the details of the settler with name X

------------
'c' Construct
lists blueprints you have the resources to construct
'-a' lists all blueprints regardless of cost

'c X' tries to construct a blueprint with name X 

------------
'b' Buildings
lists buildings in Settlement 

------------
'd' Day
passes a day

'd X' passes X days